[l] Russland hat jetzt eine "Safe Selfie"-Kampagne gestartet. Weil ihnen zu viele Bekloppte beim Selfie verunglueckt sind (100 Verletzungen, Dutzende von Toten).That warning comes after a string of recent selfie-related accidents. In May, a 21-year-old woman accidentally shot herself in the head in Moscow while taking a selfie holding a pistol. She suffered injuries but survived.Das ist ja auch mal herbe. Da war wohl nicht genug Hirn, das haette verletzt werden koennen.In January, two young men died in the Urals while taking a selfie holding a hand grenade with the pin pulled out. The mobile phone with the selfie survived as a record.Hey, Igor, ich hab hier ne Handgranate, lass uns damit mal ein Selfie machen!1!!In May, a teenager in the Ryazan region died while attempting to photograph himself as he climbed on a railway bridge and accidentally came into contact with live electrical wires.m(Hier ist uebrigens das PDF fuer den grossartigen Flyer des Innenministeriums dazu.
